<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>dmj.one Official Letterhead</title>
        <style>
            /* Default styles for the webpage */
            body {
                font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                position: relative;
            }

            header,
            footer {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
                position: fixed;
            }

            header {
                top: 0;
                padding: 10px 2cm;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            }

            header .logo {
                display: inline-block;
                vertical-align: middle;
            }

            header .details {
                display: inline-block;
                vertical-align: middle;
                text-align: left;
                margin-left: 10px;
            }

            header .details h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
                margin: 0;
            }

            header .details p {
                margin: 2px 0;
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            footer {
                bottom: 0;                
                border-top: 1px solid #000;
                font-size: 12px;
                color: #555;
            }

            footer p {
                margin: 2px 0;
            }

            main {
                margin: 150px 2cm 50px;
            }

            /* Watermark styles */
            @media print {
                @page {
                    size: A4;
                    margin: 2cm;
                }

                body::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: fixed;
                    top: 50%;
                    left: 50%;
                    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
                    width: 300px;
                    /* Adjust size as needed */
                    height: 300px;
                    /* Adjust size as needed */
                    background: url('/logo.png') no-repeat center;
                    background-size: contain;
                    opacity: 0.1;
                    z-index: 9999;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <header>
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="/logo.png" alt="dmj.one Logo" height="60">
            </div>
            <div class="details">
                <h1>dmj.one</h1>
                <p>Dream. Manifest. Journey. Together as one.</p>
                <p>Email: support@dmj.one | Website: https://dmj.one</p>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main>
            <p>Insert the main content of your letter or document here. This section will contain the actual text of the letter.</p>
        </main>
        <footer>
            <p>dmj.one | Dream. Manifest. Journey. Together as one.</p>
            <p>Email: support@dmj.one | Website: https://dmj.one</p>
            <p>Disclaimer: This document is confidential and intended for the recipient only.</p>
        </footer>
    </body>

</html>